Description: Provides tools for computing fishing mortalityâ€“based spawning potential ratio (SPR) reference points for Tier 4 groundfish stock assessments used by the North Pacific Fishery Management Council. The package supports single-species and multispecies per-recruit analyses, sensitivity evaluation of key biological and fishery assumptions, and generation of report-ready graphics for stock assessments.
